amily: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \"><b>4</b><b>）书页设计精致，有趣。</b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0); \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \">少儿教育一定要以兴趣为先行，往往一本书的封面就决定了孩子们是否会喜欢学习这个课程。本书设计精美而有趣，是儿童喜爱的风格。练习环节的设置同样多样而有趣，在快乐的学习氛围中掌握自然拼读的规律。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0); \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \"><b>5</b><b>）配套资源丰富，完备。</b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0); \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \">相关资源配套完备，包括闪卡，配套音频CD，练习册，配套软件，单词表，教材单元结构分析，语言能力分析手册，家长手册，各级别教案范例等。保障教学活动的顺利进行，可作为一套成熟的教学系统进行直接应用。为使用者免去由于二次研发造成的大量教研成本和时间的投入。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0); \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \"><b>6</b><b>）特别设置</b><b>sight words(</b><b>常用字</b><b>)</b><b>。</b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0); \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;</b>Phonics和sight words是儿童早期阅读的两大基础，但大多数自然拼读教材都忽略了sight words的重要性，没有相关内容的设置。本书按级别从歌曲和阅读中提取出现的常用字，并列成表格，方便教学。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0); \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \"><b>7</b><b>）精美的配套绘本阅读。</b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><font color=\"#3352cc\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; \"><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 0, 0); \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial microsoft yahei simsun sans-serif\'; font-size: medium; border-collapse: separate; \"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; \">精美的系列绘本阅读让学生在学习了自然拼读的基础上，学以致用，增强阅读能力。同时，每个绘本都是一个艺术的小殿堂，独具特色的艺术风格并配以经典故事，在第一时间就会抓住学生的注意力，让学生们爱不释手，成为他们成长的好伙伴。精美的阅读本不仅可以作为语音课程学习的有效补充，也可以独立作为初学英语的小朋友的阅读材料。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></span></b></font></span></span></span></b></font></span></span></div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n		<div style=\"color: rgb(51, 82, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; \">\r\n			<span style=\"color: rgb(73, 11, 252); font-family: Calibri, 宋体; font-weight: bold; \">教学资源配置:</span></div>\r\n		<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, 宋体; \">\r\n			<b>学生资源</b></p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2012-04-29 11:28:13','http://img.kooobao.cn/storage/company_website/book/phonics/smart_phonics/logo.gif','Smart Phonics','2010版全新登陆！配合多种多媒体手段，精心安排的教学流程。最适合课堂使用的Phonics教材','5',18),(351,'<div class=\"section_part_title\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; text-align: left; color: rgb(255, 102, 51); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: top; margin-top: 2px; margin-right: 2px; margin-bottom: 2px; margin-left: 2px; padding-top: 2px; padding-right: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 2px; \">\r\n	<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/course/wte.htm\" style=\"display: block; text-decoration: none; \">Sight Word Kids</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"section_part_desc\" style=\"font-family: Calibri, 宋体; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; margin-top: 2px; margin-right: 2px; margin-bottom: 2px; margin-left: 2px; padding-top: 2px; padding-right: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 2px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); \">\r\n	<div class=\"section_part_subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 17, 34); \">\r\n		轻松学英语，快乐背单词</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin-top: 5px; \">\r\n		<b>出版社: Eastwest Books</b></div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin-top: 5px; \">\r\n		<b>适用年龄:</b>&nbsp;5-10岁</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin-top: 5px; \">\r\n		<b>册数:</b>&nbsp;全套五个级别，共十册书</div>\r\n	<div style=\"margin-top: 5px; \">\r\n		<p class=\"ptitle\" style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(73, 11, 252); \">\r\n			书籍特色：</p>\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 27px; font-size: large; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><strong><font color=\"#ff0000\">Sight Words (常用字)是什么？</font><br />\r\n			* 在儿童英文中，出现频率很高的单词<br />\r\n			* 百分之五十到八十在会话或阅读上都会用到的单词<br />\r\n			* 助词或文法上的一些用字，还包含了不少的介词或代名词<br />\r\n			* 许多不规则发音的单字，如：are、go、 to...</strong></span></p>\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; \"><strong><font color=\"#ff0000\">为什么从小就要学 Sight Words？</font></strong></font></span></p>\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \">\r\n			<br />\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; \"><strong>&ldquo;Phonics 字母拼读&rdquo;与&ldquo;Sight Words常用字&rdquo; 是英语学习最重要的两大基石，完整学习后，才能为孩子在英语路上堆叠起成功的步骤。</strong></font></span></p>\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \">\r\n			<br />\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; \">学习 Sight Words 仅靠强制性的记忆是不够的，而是可以通过情境、念谣、游戏等加深孩子的印象，通过活动和练习学习到常用字的用法。</font></span></p>\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \">\r\n			<br />\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; \">东西图书出版的 Sight Word Kids 全套五级，可以配合 Love English 、 Phonics Kids 及 We Sing We Play，为幼儿园及培训中心打造丰富多彩的幼儿英语教学环境。每本书都配有视频教学DVD或者VCD，也适合家长在家自己辅导孩子。<br />\r\n			&nbsp;<br />\r\n			&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n			系列配置 - 学生部分：每级分A、 B两册</font></span></p>\r\n		<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; \">Sight Word Kids 阅读常用字 1A 1B&nbsp; 2书+2AVCD<br />\r\n			Sight Word Kids 阅读常用字 2A 2B&nbsp; 2书+2AVCD<br />\r\n			Sight Word Kids 阅读常用字 3A 3B&nbsp; 2书+2AVCD<br />\r\n			Sight Word Kids 阅读常用字 4A 4B&nbsp; 2书+2AVCD<br />\r\n			Sight Word Kids 阅读常用字 5A 5B&nbsp;&nbsp;2书+2AVCD<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			说明：<br />\r\n			1) AVCD光盘同时具备CD和VCD功能，可当作CD或VCD使用。<br />\r\n			2) 全套5级10册，每册能学习到20个左右常用字的用法，而不是简单的背诵记忆，对英语阅读能力提高带来极大帮助。<br />\r\n			&nbsp;<br />\r\n			&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n			可选购的系列配置 - 教师部分：<br />\r\n			We Sing、Phonics、Sight Word 教学指导手册 Power Reading</font></span></p>\r\n		<p class=\"ptitle\" style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(73, 11, 252); \">\r\n			教学资源配置:</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<b>学生资源</b></p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2012-04-29 12:15:07','http://img.kooobao.cn/storage/company_website/book/sight_word/swk/logo.gif','Sight Word Kids','幼儿常用字教材 220个神奇的常用字，带领孩子提前进入英语阅读领域！','4',19);
